WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.400
[Anna] Hello, my name is Anna. I am 23 years old.

00:05.400 --> 00:09.200
[Anna] I am from Italy. I am a student.

00:10.200 --> 00:16.000
[Mark] Hi, Anna. I am Mark. I am 30. I am from Canada.

00:16.500 --> 00:20.700
[Mark] I am an engineer. I work in a big company.

00:21.700 --> 00:28.900
[Kate] Nice to meet you. My name is Kate. I am 26. I am from the UK. I am a teacher.

00:29.800 --> 00:33.300
[Anna] Kate, where do you live? Do you live in a house?

00:34.300 --> 00:40.800
[Kate] No, I live in a small flat in London. I live here with my cat. Mark, do you have a big family?

00:41.800 --> 00:48.800
[Mark] Yes, I do. I have a wife and two brothers. We live in a big house with a garden.

00:49.300 --> 00:50.800
[Mark] Anna, what about you?

00:51.800 --> 00:56.500
[Anna] I live with my parents and my sister. Our house is near the university.

00:57.100 --> 00:59.600
[Mark] Anna, what is your daily routine?

01:00.600 --> 01:07.600
[Anna] I get up at 7 o'clock. I drink orange juice and go to my classes. I study all day.

01:08.600 --> 01:16.600
[Kate] I get up early too. I go to school and help my pupils. In the evening, I am tired. I like to cook dinner.

01:17.600 --> 01:22.600
[Mark] I get up at 8 o'clock. I drink strong coffee. I work from 9 to 5.

01:22.700 --> 01:24.700
[Anna] What do you like to eat for dinner?

01:25.700 --> 01:30.700
[Kate] I love Italian food. I like pizza and pasta. I drink tea with lemon.

01:31.700 --> 01:36.700
[Mark] I like fish and vegetables. I don't like meat. I drink a lot of water.

01:37.700 --> 01:41.700
[Anna] I like fruit and salad. My favorite drink is milk.

01:42.700 --> 01:45.700
[Kate] Mark, what are your hobbies?

01:45.800 --> 01:46.800
[Kate] What do you do on weekends?

01:47.800 --> 01:54.800
[Mark] I like photos. I take many pictures of nature. I also like swimming. And you, Anna?

01:55.800 --> 02:03.800
[Anna] I love music. I play the guitar. Sometimes I go to the cinema with my sister.

02:04.800 --> 02:07.800
[Kate] That is great. I like books and long walks in the park.

02:08.800 --> 02:12.800
[Mark] It is very interesting. Nice to meet you.

02:13.800 --> 02:14.800
[Anna] Nice to meet you too.

02:15.700 --> 02:17.800
[Kate] Have a nice day.
